<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c4">[٥١٣١]</span> فَلَا تقربن بِفَتْح رَاء قَوْله<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>